        "workedSolution": "The transit route is the corridor travelled between the generating region and the destination region, including the airports, roads and stopovers used along the way.\nThe hub airport is used only to pass through, so it lies on the transit route. It is not the source of the tourists, nor the place where the holiday is spent.",
